John the Ripper:

John the Ripper is a password cracking tool.

Installation:

sudo apt-get -y install build-essential libssl-dev git zlib1g-dev
git clone git://github.com/magnumripper/JohnTheRipper -b bleeding-jumbo john
./configure && make -s clean && make -sj4

Usage:

john --wordlist= <hashfile> | using wordlist
john --format=Raw-MD5 <hashfile> | format of the hash, example MD5
